### Enroll in a course
POST http://localhost:3000/api/enrollments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "courseId": "COURSE_ID_HERE"
}

### Get enrolled courses
GET http://localhost:3000/api/enrollments/my-courses
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get course progress
GET http://localhost:3000/api/enrollments/COURSE_ID/progress
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Mark lesson as completed
POST http://localhost:3000/api/enrollments/COURSE_ID/lessons/LESSON_ID/complete
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Take a quiz
POST http://localhost:3000/api/quizzes/QUIZ_ID/attempt
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "answers": [
    {
      "questionId": "q1",
      "answer": 1
    },
    {
      "questionId": "q2",
      "answer": 0
    }
  ]
}

### Get quiz results
GET http://localhost:3000/api/quizzes/QUIZ_ID/results
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Submit course review
POST http://localhost:3000/api/courses/COURSE_ID/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Excellent course! Very well structured and informative."
}